snippet.title: Goober Dash - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Online: http://www.gooberdash.io
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gooberdash/id6470684038
Android: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.winterpixel.gooberdash
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2661160/Goober_Dash

Introducing GOOBER DASH! Winterpixel Games' latest multiplayer experience! Dive into the adrenaline-pumping world of a 32-player platformer racing royale. Run, Jump and Dash to outmaneuver the field in this epic race to the finish line!

Customize your Goobers with a wide array of unlockable outfits, emotes, and celebration moves, making every race a unique and stylish experience!

But that's not all - Goober Dash empowers you to become the creator of your own destiny. With a full-featured level editor, craft, share, and conquer your very own custom levels. Dive into the best community-created courses, and compete to claim the top times on each one.

https://twitter.com/winterpixelco
https://www.winterpixel.com
https://www.tiktok.com/@winterpixelco
https://www.twitch.tv/winterpixelco
